Package: PridePalettes
Title: Color Palettes Based on Pride Flags
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joel",
           family = "Le Forestier",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joel.leforestier@mail.utoronto.ca")
Description: Use color schemes from Pride flags in ggplot2 graphs by wrapping the pride_palette() function inside scale_color_manual or scale_fill_manual arguments. Or, generate pre-made Pride flags using the flag() function.
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 3.3.1)
